      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding weekend project or a budget-friendly starter? This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back on the road, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a great value on a parts car! It's an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right owner.",
